WEBVTT

00:01.700 --> 00:03.590
《越狱》前情回顾
previously on prison break

00:03.600 --> 00:05.920
嘿  我们上路了
Hey,yo,we're headed out man.

00:05.930 --> 00:07.750
祝你们好运
Good luck.

00:07.760 --> 00:09.350
希望你可以找回你女朋友
I hope you find the girl,buddy.

00:09.360 --> 00:11.090
亲爱的 出什么事了?
Baby,what the hell is going on?

00:11.100 --> 00:13.390
赫克托说你不能假释
Yeah,well Hector says that you can serve your full sentence.

00:13.400 --> 00:15.220
你来这干什么? 玛丽克鲁兹在哪?
What are you doing here,where's Maricruz?

00:15.230 --> 00:16.590
她现在是我的女人了
She's with me now.

00:16.600 --> 00:18.890
我听说你马上能回家了?
What's this I hear about you coming home soon?

00:18.900 --> 00:20.990
你可别再让女儿失望了
You're not getting your daughter's hopes up are you?

00:21.000 --> 00:22.920
你坐稳了吗?
You sitting down?

00:22.930 --> 00:24.950
这周我就能回家了
Your man is coming home this week.

00:24.960 --> 00:27.450
我们可以从这里步行去法院
e can make it to the courthouse on foot from here.

00:27.460 --> 00:29.390
你不明白 所有的东西都在里面
You don't understand,everything is in that car.

00:29.400 --> 00:32.290
我戒毒已经18个月了
I've been clean for 18 months now.

00:32.300 --> 00:33.720
我想用自己的亲身经历
I want to help people get

00:33.730 --> 00:37.060
帮助那些失足朋友从迷失中回来
from where I've been to where I am.

00:39.660 --> 00:40.690
没错
You were right.

00:40.700 --> 00:42.420
我不该把你也卷进来
I should never have gotten you involved in this.

00:42.430 --> 00:45.590
我只是想知道迈克尔·斯科菲尔德
I just need to know what Michael Scofield

00:45.600 --> 00:48.120
帮你拿绿卡的条件是什么
wanted from you in exchange for the green card.

00:48.130 --> 00:49.720
卡罗琳 我干这行已经15年了
Caroline,I've been doing this for 15 years

00:49.730 --> 00:51.890
所有的事情都是为了你
and it's never been about anything other than you,

00:51.900 --> 00:54.820
为了你的家庭 最重要的是为了这个国家
your family and,most importantly,this country.

00:54.830 --> 00:57.020
我需要知道我在为谁卖命
Now,I need to know who I'm working for here.

00:57.030 --> 00:59.190
你在为我效力
You are working for me.

00:59.200 --> 01:00.320
你是否知道任何有关
Are you aware of any arrangement

01:00.330 --> 01:01.990
贝利克警官和罪犯之间
Officer Bellick had

01:02.000 --> 01:04.090
关于监狱工厂工作安排的内幕?
with any inmate regarding Prison Industries?

01:04.100 --> 01:06.290
是的 他把这个权利卖给了约翰 阿布鲁奇
Yeah,he sold it to John Abruzzi.

01:06.300 --> 01:08.290
布拉德 贝利克
Officer Brad Bellick,

01:08.300 --> 01:10.550
辞退原职 立即生效
you're terminated,  <i>effective immediately.

01:10.560 --> 01:13.750
电视台刚刚宣布了悬赏
They just announced the rewards on the TV.

01:13.760 --> 01:15.490
有多少?
How much?

01:15.500 --> 01:17.650
每个悬赏10万美元
$100,000 a piece.

01:17.660 --> 01:22.960
钱就埋在犹他
The money is just outside of Tooele,Utah.

01:25.500 --> 01:26.710
上卡车!
Truck!

01:32.330 --> 01:33.650
派人去这附近所有的医院
Get men in all the area hospitals.

01:33.660 --> 01:35.520
不管他们在哪里 有一个伤得很重
Wherever they are,one of them is bleeding good.

01:35.530 --> 01:36.890
我们必须继续跑
We got to move.

01:36.900 --> 01:40.060
我不行了
I can't.

01:43.900 --> 01:46.390
费尽心思实施越狱计划
You put in all that work,break out of prison,

01:46.400 --> 01:49.150
却没想在这阴沟翻船
only to end up dead at the bottom of a ditch.

01:49.160 --> 01:50.950
听上去有点伤悲
Kind of sad really.

01:51.700 --> 01:53.050
出事的是谁?
So which one of them was it?

01:56.330 --> 02:00.480
十二小时前

02:04.930 --> 02:06.920
每个诊所都派人手监控了
We've got a blanket on all the hospitals.

02:06.930 --> 02:08.020
免费小诊所呢?
Free clinics?

02:08.030 --> 02:09.320
只要是有创可贴和消毒剂的
If they've got Band-Aids and Bactine,

02:09.330 --> 02:10.520
我们都派人去了
we've got a body in there.

02:10.530 --> 02:11.850
只要那两兄弟来医治
The brothers come in for medical,

02:11.860 --> 02:14.550
就会被押送回福克斯河
they're getting it in a van on the way back to Fox River.

02:14.560 --> 02:16.850
另外六个有突破吗?
Anything break on the other six?

02:16.860 --> 02:18.390
已经监控他们的家庭了
Eyes and ears on the families.

02:18.400 --> 02:20.520
目前还没有 或许都躲起来了
So far,no hits. Maybe just laying low.

02:20.530 --> 02:23.120
对罪犯而言什么事情最难办到?
What's the hardest thing in the world for a con to do?

02:23.130 --> 02:24.450
没有吧?
Nothing?

02:24.460 --> 02:26.420
生命中有些事是注定的 你是？
Few things in life are certain,Ms....?

02:26.430 --> 02:27.750
-我姓兰 -死亡 税收
Lang. Death,taxes

02:27.760 --> 02:29.690
事实上逃犯很容易......
and the fact that a man on the run

02:29.700 --> 02:32.250
......在最初的72小时内犯错误
will make a mistake sometime in the first 72 hours.

02:32.260 --> 02:33.950
需要赶路 他会去偷车
Needing distance,he'll steal a car.

02:33.960 --> 02:35.390
需要钱 他会去抢劫
Needing money,he'll rob a store.

02:35.400 --> 02:38.290
需要帮助 他会去信任不该相信之人
Needing help,he'll trust someone that he shouldn't.

02:38.300 --> 02:40.020
一旦他这么做
And when he does...

02:40.030 --> 02:44.360
就会留下蛛丝马迹助我们顺藤摸瓜
he <i>will leave behind the crumbs that will take us right to him.

02:50.240 --> 02:51.440
我需要你帮忙
I need your help.

02:51.450 --> 02:52.350
迈克尔你在干吗?
Michael,what are you doing?

02:52.360 --> 02:54.970
-辣椒粉  -什么?
Cayenne pepper. What?

02:56.230 --> 02:58.150
厨房里有吗?
In your kitchen,do you have any?

02:58.160 --> 03:00.350
呃...或许有吧
Um... yeah,maybe.

03:00.360 --> 03:03.650
我需要些外用酒精、毛巾
I'm gonna need some rubbing alcohol,some towels

03:03.660 --> 03:05.450
还有止痛药 有用的都拿来
and pain killers,whatever you got.

03:05.460 --> 03:06.850
再来点酒
Some booze.

03:06.860 --> 03:08.250
拜托!
Please!

03:13.860 --> 03:17.900
别紧张 放松
Easy,easy,easy,easy.

03:22.200 --> 03:23.820
我没事  我们走吧
It's fine,man,let's just keep moving.

03:23.830 --> 03:26.490
我们继续跑 血就止不住
We keep moving and that leg keeps bleeding.

03:26.500 --> 03:28.450
血如果止不住
The leg keeps bleeding

03:28.460 --> 03:30.620
我们根本逃不出伊利诺斯州
and we're not getting out of Illinois.

03:30.630 --> 03:33.350
会很疼
This is going to hurt.

03:33.360 --> 03:37.700
很好 忍一下
That's good,that's good,that's good.

03:38.960 --> 03:40.620
这样能封住毛细血管
This will seal the capillaries.

03:41.430 --> 03:42.790
迈克尔  你不该来这里
Michael,you should not have come here.

03:42.800 --> 03:44.250
警察来这问过话了
The police have been here asking questions.

03:44.260 --> 03:45.320
我们别无选择
We didn't have a choice.

03:45.330 --> 03:46.350
听着
Listen,you know I'm thankful

03:46.360 --> 03:47.850
我很感激你帮我获得绿卡
for the help with the green card,

03:47.860 --> 03:50.350
但是我不想卷进来
but I just don't want to get involved. I know,I know it wasn't part

03:50.360 --> 03:52.420
我知道这不是我们原来说好的
of our deal,I know,I know. Yes.

03:52.430 --> 03:56.010
抱歉 真的很抱歉
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

03:56.720 --> 03:57.700
但我们没其它地方可去
But there was nowhere else to go.

03:57.710 --> 04:00.450
我看到新闻的时候很担心
When I saw you on the news,I was worried.

04:00.460 --> 04:02.990
我真希望你现在已经越过国境
I just hoped you crossed the border by now.

04:03.720 --> 04:04.620
我也是
So did I.

04:07.830 --> 04:09.590
不停的给他上药
Keep giving him these.

04:09.600 --> 04:11.450
看看能否帮他弄身干净衣服
See if you can find him some clean clothes.

04:11.460 --> 04:13.020
好
Okay.

04:13.030 --> 04:15.890
我必须回去把车弄回来
I got to go back and get our car.

04:15.900 --> 04:17.820
别管那车了
Forget the car.

04:17.830 --> 04:18.890
另外搞一辆就是了
We can get another.

04:18.900 --> 04:21.020
我需要的不是一辆车而是我们那辆车
I don't need <i>a car,I need <i>that car.

04:21.030 --> 04:22.420
为什么?
Why?

04:22.430 --> 04:30.630
所有可以帮我们销声匿迹 的东西都在那辆车上
Because in that car is everything we need to disappear.

05:10.200 --> 05:11.290
有什么新发现?
What have you got?

05:11.300 --> 05:12.690
是这么回事
Here we go boss,one of the blues

05:12.700 --> 05:14.920
有个兄弟几小时前抓了个流浪汉
hauled in a vagrant a couple hours ago.

05:14.930 --> 05:17.700
这几件东西似乎都不属于他
Seems the man was in possession of an item or two that didn't exactly belong to him.

05:30.500 --> 05:32.540
看来我们已经逮到第一个错误了
Looks like we got our first mistake.

06:17.760 --> 06:20.250
嘿 有没有日式牛肉干?
Hey,you got any of that oriental jerky?

06:20.260 --> 06:22.190
什么?
Excuse me?

06:22.200 --> 06:24.230
红烧味的
Teriyaki flavor.

06:25.420 --> 06:26.190
没有
No.

06:27.000 --> 06:28.240
仓库里有没有?
You got any in the back?

06:30.580 --> 06:31.620
呃 我看看
Uh,let me check.

06:31.700 --> 06:34.950
伙计 顺便再给我弄瓶老酒
And,uh,give me a bottle of that Early Times while you're back there,junior.

06:34.960 --> 06:36.490
今天给你赚到了
Feel free to earn your paycheck today.

06:36.500 --> 06:38.320
看好店 我马上回来
Watch the store,I'll be right back.

06:45.000 --> 06:46.520
最近怎么样 罗伊?
How goes it,Roy?

06:57.400 --> 06:58.920
实话告诉你
To be honest,Roy,I could've done

06:58.930 --> 07:00.550
我用一根手指就可以搞定你
without the knee to the junk.

07:00.560 --> 07:02.520
你居然咬我 布拉德
You bit me,Brad.

07:02.530 --> 07:04.150
就像个小姑娘似的
Like a little girl,you bite me.

07:04.160 --> 07:05.620
这是你自找的
Well,you had it coming.

07:05.630 --> 07:07.370
或许吧
Yeah,probably did.

07:08.700 --> 07:10.350
我们竟然为这种事打架
You know it's crazy,us taking it out

07:10.360 --> 07:11.990
听上去真的很疯狂
on each other for how things turned out.

07:12.000 --> 07:14.750
要怪的话  就该怪那些犯人
You want someone to blame,how about those convicts

07:14.760 --> 07:17.650
每天起来看到的都是他们的报道
staring up at us from the papers every morning.

07:17.660 --> 07:19.520
他们害我丢了工作
They took my job,

07:19.530 --> 07:23.550
我的养老金、尊严都没了
my pension,my dignity.

07:23.560 --> 07:24.790
当他们翻过那堵墙的时候
When they went over that wall,

07:24.800 --> 07:26.620
他们把一切都带走了
they took all of it right along with them.

07:26.630 --> 07:28.860
带走了我奋斗了一辈子的东西
Everything I worked  for my whole life.

07:30.200 --> 07:32.550
看到悬赏了吗?
See that reward they got?

07:32.560 --> 07:35.590
这帮混蛋死了都比我们活着值钱
Those ass-hats are worth more dead than you and I are alive.

07:35.600 --> 07:37.050
不用多久了
Not for long.

07:37.060 --> 07:38.550
什么意思?
What do you mean?

07:38.560 --> 07:41.730
我是说有人会得到这笔悬赏 好比是我
I mean somebody's going to get that money,might as well be me.

07:44.930 --> 07:46.250
像那样的抓捕工作
You know a job like that

07:46.260 --> 07:49.120
如果多个帮手会更容易些
might go a little smoother with an extra pair of hands.

07:49.130 --> 07:51.590
你真认为我会和你分享那笔赏金?
You really think I'm going to split that reward with you?

07:51.600 --> 07:53.490
当你遇到他们的时候
I'm just saying,you run into those brothers,

07:53.500 --> 07:55.720
双拳难敌四手
two of them,one of you.

07:55.730 --> 07:58.260
到时候你就知道有帮手的好处了
You might find yourself wishing for a good wingman.

08:13.380 --> 08:14.520
快去搞定它 麦克
Just get it done,Mike.

08:16.900 --> 08:17.950
你好
How are you doing?

08:17.960 --> 08:19.420
有事吗?
May I help you?

08:19.430 --> 08:21.930
是的 恰克
Yeah,I hope so,Chuck.

08:23.290 --> 08:24.620
我想你们可能拖走了我的车
I think you may have towed my car.

08:25.890 --> 08:26.740
什么样的车?
What did it look like?

08:26.750 --> 08:28.180
什么样的车?
What did it look like?

08:28.190 --> 08:30.090
就是你偷背包的车
The car you stole the backpack from.

08:30.100 --> 08:31.270
什么样的车?
What did it look like?

08:32.320 --> 08:35.100
我记不清了 或许是灰色的吧
I don't know,man,maybe it was gray.

08:35.120 --> 08:36.410
灰色的雅阁
It's a gray Accord.

08:37.460 --> 08:38.310
车牌号?
License number?

08:38.320 --> 08:39.860
我就知道这些了
Look,man,that's all I know.

08:39.870 --> 08:41.260
我不是去偷车的
I wasn't after the car.

08:42.270 --> 08:44.210
我还以为包里会有些衣服
Thought the bag had some clothes in it.

08:44.790 --> 08:46.280
还记得车停在哪吗?
You remember where The car was parked?

08:46.290 --> 08:47.110
你停哪的?
Where'd you park it?

08:48.380 --> 08:50.000
汉考克大街和十五大道的拐角
Corner of Hancock and 15th.

08:50.530 --> 08:52.370
我不知道 或许在十五大道附近吧
I don't know,maybe around 15th somewhere,

08:53.220 --> 08:54.490
但是现在肯定不在那了
but it ain't going to be there anymore.

08:55.760 --> 08:57.180
-此话怎讲?  -那就是为什么我没有机会
What do you mean? That's the reason I didn't get

08:57.190 --> 08:58.700
再弄些其他的东西
to grab anything else.

08:59.370 --> 09:00.660
被拖车拖走了
Tow truck rolls up.

09:01.200 --> 09:01.950
已经在查了
Already on it.

09:04.530 --> 09:06.980
60块拖车费
It's going to be 60 bucks for the tow,

09:07.900 --> 09:09.110
24块过夜费
and 24 for the overnight.

09:22.880 --> 09:25.000
好了 我去把你的车开来
All right,be right back with your vehicle.

09:25.020 --> 09:26.230
再等几分钟
Shouldn't take but a few minutes.

09:37.230 --> 09:37.820
喂
Hello?

09:37.830 --> 09:39.110
佩特 是我苏克雷
Petey,it's Sucre.

09:39.640 --> 09:41.410
是费尔南多 苏克雷吗?
As in,Fernando Sucre?

09:41.770 --> 09:43.720
-难道还会有别的?  -但愿没有
Is there another one? Man,I hope not.

09:44.190 --> 09:47.060
但是我的兄弟苏克雷不会给我打电话
But my boy Sucre would not be calling me on the telephone,

09:47.070 --> 09:50.920
他知道这会让我成为他潜逃的从犯
thereby making me an accessory to <i>his dumb-ass escape,man.

09:50.930 --> 09:52.540
我很抱歉 我只是...
I-I'm sorry,bro,I just...

09:52.940 --> 09:55.310
我只是希望你帮我联系玛丽克鲁兹
I just... I just need you to get a hold of Maricruz.

09:55.320 --> 09:56.510
我不能给她打电话
I can't call her cell

09:56.520 --> 09:58.690
因为探员肯定监听的
because the Feds will be all over the place...

09:58.700 --> 09:59.360
听着
Homie,listen,man,

09:59.370 --> 10:01.370
忘了那女孩吧
you have got to forget about that girl.

10:01.380 --> 10:03.150
如果我能忘了她
If I could forget about her,<i>pendejo,

10:03.160 --> 10:04.340
我就会在监狱里
I'd still be at Fox River,

10:04.340 --> 10:06.110
老老实实把刑服完
sitting in cell 40 on your old bunk.

10:06.500 --> 10:07.800
我希望你站稳了
Yeah,well,I hope you're holding on

10:07.820 --> 10:10.580
我有个坏消息
to something tight 'cause I'm about to break it down for you,brother.

10:10.890 --> 10:12.150
她要和赫克托结婚了
She's getting married to Hector

10:12.780 --> 10:13.520
就在星期六
on Saturday.

10:15.420 --> 10:16.190
今天星期几?
What day is today?

10:16.530 --> 10:17.330
周四
Thursday,bro.

10:17.800 --> 10:18.440
很遗憾
Sorry,man.

10:23.320 --> 10:26.890
不管了 今晚你务必把她带到你家
All right,you got to get her to your place tonight.

10:26.900 --> 10:28.280
等等...
Hang on,man...

10:28.290 --> 10:29.960
我只有最后一次机会改变她的决定了
I got one last shot to make her change her mind,dude.

10:30.570 --> 10:32.610
帮我找到她 好不好?
Just find a way to get her there,okay?

10:33.040 --> 10:34.970
等等...苏克雷 别挂
Wait...

11:08.810 --> 11:09.980
关于这个 呃...
About the,uh...

11:09.980 --> 11:11.240
这个打破的窗
about the broken window.

11:12.000 --> 11:14.310
我们在那墙上贴有免责声明
Yeah,we got a disclaimer posted right there on the wall,says we're not responsible...

11:14.320 --> 11:15.500
我不在乎... 不在乎...
Yeah,I don't... I don't... I don't care

11:15.510 --> 11:17.610
我不在乎窗户
about the broken window,Chuck.

11:20.370 --> 11:21.700
我里面有个背包不见了
I had a backpack inside.

11:23.200 --> 11:24.180
拖来的时候就没了
Not when we got it.

11:25.200 --> 11:26.620
还要麻烦你填几张表
I got some paperwork for you to fill out.

11:32.110 --> 11:32.860
你看上去很眼熟
You look familiar.

11:36.960 --> 11:41.220
我刚来的时候你在这里当医生
Yeah,you... you were the attending when I first started here.

11:41.910 --> 11:42.510
原来如此
Sure.

11:44.120 --> 11:47.410
能帮我叫辆出租车吗?
Um,would one of you mind calling me a cab,please?

11:48.470 --> 11:49.530
我看不必了
I don't think so.

11:51.920 --> 11:53.480
唐克雷蒂医生
Look,Dr. Tancredi,I...

11:54.810 --> 11:56.060
祝你好运
I just want to say good luck.

11:56.070 --> 11:57.080
莎拉 唐克雷蒂?
Sara Tancredi?

11:57.090 --> 11:59.550
很抱歉 你有权保持沉默
I'm sorry. You have the right to remain silent.

11:59.560 --> 12:01.010
请把手放在后面
Please place your hands behind your back.

12:02.170 --> 12:03.770
如果你有任何疑问 我愿意去...
If you have any questions,I'm happy to come down to...

12:03.780 --> 12:05.640
唐克雷蒂  出于对你父亲的尊重
Ms. Tancredi,out of respect for your father,

12:06.220 --> 12:07.390
我再说一次 手放后面
I'm going to ask you again.

12:07.400 --> 12:08.560
我父亲?
My father?

12:08.570 --> 12:12.370
我相信他不希望把事情闹大
I'm sure he'd prefer that this went without incident.

12:12.370 --> 12:13.930
在回答警察问题前
You have the right to speak to an attorney

12:13.940 --> 12:15.410
你有权先和律师沟通
before you speak to the police.

12:15.420 --> 12:18.670
你所说的一切可能会成为呈堂证供
Anything you say may be used against you in a court of law.

12:19.470 --> 12:22.250
审讯期间可以要求律师在场
And to have an attorney present during questioning now or in the future.

12:24.440 --> 12:25.730
卡罗琳  警察把她带走了
Caroline,they're taking her in.

12:27.970 --> 12:29.170
当然  我会盯住她的
Of course. I'll keep an eye on her.

12:32.850 --> 12:34.980
在下面签个名...
All you got to do is sign here at the bottom...

12:36.220 --> 12:36.990
然后就能走了
and be on your way.

12:38.200 --> 12:38.920
不好意思
Excuse me,please.

12:41.750 --> 12:42.580
布鲁斯特拖车行
Brewster's Towing.

12:42.590 --> 12:45.290
我是FBI的探员马宏
This is Agent Mahone with the Federal Bureau of Investigation.

12:45.300 --> 12:46.160
你怎么称呼?
Who am I speaking with?

12:47.550 --> 12:48.350
恰克
Chuck.

12:48.360 --> 12:51.080
好的 恰克  请你留意一个可能的情形
Okay,Chuck,I want to alert you to a possible situation.

12:51.090 --> 12:52.030
你在听我说吗 恰克?
Are you listening to me,Chuck?

12:52.030 --> 12:54.590
可能会有人去你那里找一辆车
An individual may be coming there to inquire about a vehicle.

12:54.600 --> 12:57.700
一辆灰色雅阁车 或许车窗还砸碎了
A gray Accord,probably with a busted rear window.

12:57.990 --> 13:01.000
有没有人来找我说的那辆车?
Has anyone come by looking for a vehicle that matches that description?

13:06.920 --> 13:07.740
是的 老板
Yes,sir.

13:08.570 --> 13:09.240
什么时候?
When?

13:12.420 --> 13:13.160
呃...
Uh...

13:14.010 --> 13:14.560
恰克
Chuck.

13:14.570 --> 13:15.950
你告诉我 他什么时候来的?
Will you tell me when he was there?

13:18.800 --> 13:19.940
就是现在
Right now.

13:28.940 --> 13:31.140
斯科菲尔德就在那个拖车行
Brewster's towing.Scofield's there.

13:31.150 --> 13:32.200
恰克拖住他
Chuck,stall him.

13:32.210 --> 13:34.690
我们已派人手过来了 不要让他跑了
We've got people on the way-- do not let him leave.

13:35.350 --> 13:36.440
不要让他跑了
Do not let him leave.

13:36.450 --> 13:38.220
是我的老板 他...
It's my supervisor,he's,he...

13:38.230 --> 13:40.190
我得等有了许可才能放行
I just got to get clearance before,I can release the car.

13:42.440 --> 13:44.170
恰克还在吗? 嘿 恰克
Chuck,you there? Hey,Chuck.

13:44.660 --> 13:46.420
恰克还在吗?
Okay,come on,come on,Chuck,you still with me?

13:48.960 --> 13:52.620
在 等你到了那辆车或许已不在了
Yeah,that vehicle might not be here when you get here.

13:53.530 --> 13:55.000
你得现在就派人过来
You need to send somebody now.

13:55.010 --> 13:57.060
不要让他跑了!
Do not let him leave!

14:00.160 --> 14:01.250
哦！ 他拿走了钥匙
Oh,he got the keys.

14:05.980 --> 14:07.700
那帮警察都在哪儿?!
Where the hell are those units?!

14:07.710 --> 14:09.250
还要6、7分钟才能到
Still six or seven minutes out,sir.

14:15.620 --> 14:16.990
监听设备监控到富兰克林
We got chatter; it's Franklin.

14:17.000 --> 14:18.360
他在打公用电话
He's at a payphone Downtown.

14:19.100 --> 14:19.850
第二个错误了
Mistake number two.

14:23.040 --> 14:24.050
听着 我明白
Look,I know.

14:24.060 --> 14:25.750
亲爱的 我都明白 听我解释好不好?
I know,baby,just let me explain,all right?

14:26.190 --> 14:28.080
你真的当过兵吗?
Were you ever even in the military?

14:28.690 --> 14:30.900
我为国卖命 可是国家却辜负我
I served my country,and my country served me up.

14:31.560 --> 14:32.230
行了吗?
All right?

14:32.990 --> 14:35.910
我也希望现在就能把一切都告诉你
Now,look,I wish I could lay this all out for you right here,right now.

14:37.290 --> 14:38.710
但是亲爱的 真的很抱歉
But just know,baby,I am sorry,

14:38.730 --> 14:41.250
我爱你 等时机成熟
and I love you,and when the time comes,

14:41.260 --> 14:42.620
我会把一切都告诉你
I will explain everything.

14:44.530 --> 14:47.930
给我个不举报你的理由
Give me one good reason why I shouldn't turn you in right now.

14:48.530 --> 14:49.830
你知道吗? 我可以给你三个
You know what? I'll give you three.

14:50.980 --> 14:52.210
我 你
Me,you,

14:52.230 --> 14:55.270
还有可爱的女儿
and that beautiful little girl... who used to love me.

14:55.280 --> 14:56.930
我有个计划
I got a plan.

14:57.380 --> 14:58.220
我有个计划
I got a plan

14:58.640 --> 14:59.820
我先去弄些钱
that is going to get us some money,

15:00.450 --> 15:02.720
然后我们去一个
where you and I and our baby--

15:03.460 --> 15:05.920
再也没有人会找到我们的地方
nobody can ever find us or bother us again.

15:06.330 --> 15:07.160
你得相信我
You got to trust me.

15:07.610 --> 15:09.910
我现在需要你听我把话说完
That's all I need is the opportunity for you to hear me out.

15:10.230 --> 15:10.880
好吗?
All right?

15:14.680 --> 15:15.300
好吧
All right.

15:17.290 --> 15:17.980
那好 听着
All right,listen.

15:18.940 --> 15:20.890
有人试着从你那
Has anybody tried to contact you

15:21.840 --> 15:22.570
打听我的消息吗?
about me?

15:24.120 --> 15:24.780
没有
No.

15:25.360 --> 15:26.170
好
Okay.

15:26.620 --> 15:28.160
好  很好
Okay,that's good,that's good.

15:30.430 --> 15:31.070
听着
Listen.

15:32.830 --> 15:34.090
在“彩虹轩”
In the Rainbow Room...

15:35.230 --> 15:36.370
纽约的一个餐厅
Restaurant,New York City.

15:37.000 --> 15:40.310
你还记得那个地方吗?
Do you remember that beautiful spot

15:40.320 --> 15:41.350
我们拍照片的地方
where we took that picture?

15:43.290 --> 15:44.930
窗户旁边的那张
The one by the window?

15:46.150 --> 15:48.210
嗯
Mm-hmm.

15:51.320 --> 15:55.870
一周后的今天我会在那儿等着
I am going a be waiting in that spot one week from now.

15:57.620 --> 16:00.690
我现在唯一的心愿就是
And that's all that I want in this whole world

16:00.710 --> 16:02.810
我最爱的两个女人能在那等我
is for my two girls to be waiting there for me.

16:02.820 --> 16:04.480
你明白我在说些什么吗?
Do you understand what I'm saying?

16:04.810 --> 16:06.000
我要挂了
Look,I got to go.

16:07.340 --> 16:10.550
宝贝 我只想知道你会不会去?
Baby,I just want to know,are you going to be there?

16:11.180 --> 16:12.120
我不知道
I don't know.

16:14.350 --> 16:15.200
可你是了解我的啊
But you know me.

16:15.520 --> 16:16.650
--是吗?  --是的!
Do I? Yes!

16:18.680 --> 16:19.910
再见 迈尔斯
Good-bye,Miles.

16:28.350 --> 16:30.210
我会通知曼哈顿当局布控
I'll alert the field office in Manhattan

16:30.220 --> 16:31.110
把富兰克林的照片传过去
have them send Franklin's picture

16:31.120 --> 16:32.800
发给彩虹轩的每个职工
to every employee at the Rainbow Room.

16:32.810 --> 16:34.370
接着你就去找他老婆 女人跟女人谈话好办事
Then go have a chat with his wife,woman-to-woman.

16:34.370 --> 16:37.700
问她为什么从未去过福克斯河 探视他丈夫
Ask her why she never once visited her husband at Fox River.

16:37.720 --> 16:38.890
记得装做你什么也不知道的样子
Pretend you don't know the answer.

16:38.900 --> 16:40.070
这段感情很脆弱
That relationship is fragile.

16:40.070 --> 16:42.090
我们不断旁敲侧击 攻破她的心理防线
We keep tapping on cracks,and she's going to break.

16:42.630 --> 16:44.840
好的  长官 我很佩服你的方案
Yes,sir,I appreciate the assignment. I...

16:44.860 --> 16:46.130
我不需要恭维话
Lang,I don't need gratitude.

16:46.130 --> 16:48.560
我只要线索 答案和进展
I need leads,answers,progress.

16:48.570 --> 16:51.030
做不到的话就给我卷铺盖走人
Anybody that can't deliver that just don't even unpack.

16:51.370 --> 16:52.910
-明白吗? -是 长官
Clear? Yes,sir.

16:57.270 --> 16:57.880
惠勒先生
Mr. Wheeler.

16:58.540 --> 16:59.190
稍等别挂
Stand by.

16:59.200 --> 16:59.980
盯紧斯科菲尔德
Stay on Scofield.

16:59.990 --> 17:01.740
我要那辆雅阁车的车牌号
I want the license plate number on that Accord

17:01.740 --> 17:03.350
别再抱着电话不放
and I want you to get it out on the wire.

17:04.180 --> 17:04.790
好
Yeah.

17:05.820 --> 17:06.530
快！
Now.

17:06.830 --> 17:07.600
回头再说
I'll call you back.

17:14.140 --> 17:14.830
怎么了?
What's going on?

17:18.220 --> 17:20.370
显然还有其他人也在找这辆车
Apparently,I wasn't the only one looking for this car.

17:20.380 --> 17:21.070
是啊
Right.

17:21.610 --> 17:22.490
我们走吧

17:29.590 --> 17:31.140
很抱歉 把你也扯进来
I'm sorry I had to involve you in this.

17:32.220 --> 17:34.900
我是说 让你越陷越深
I mean,any more than I already have

17:38.920 --> 17:39.510
好运
Good luck.

17:41.830 --> 17:42.470
你也是
To you,too.

17:45.160 --> 17:46.080
那么...
So,um...

17:52.030 --> 17:52.780
再见了
I'll see you.

17:54.480 --> 17:55.130
但愿还能再见面
Yeah,I hope so.

18:09.790 --> 18:10.490
你还好吗?
You all right?

18:11.480 --> 18:12.230
是的
Yeah.

18:12.980 --> 18:14.030
那就好
Good.

18:15.310 --> 18:17.660
我们向西走 去拿钱 去救LJ
We're heading west,toward the money,toward LJ.

18:18.660 --> 18:20.250
在这之前还有一件事
We just got one more stop to make.

18:21.020 --> 18:21.650
什么事?
What for?

18:24.470 --> 18:25.170
你相信我吗?
You trust me?

18:26.080 --> 18:27.570
我当然相信你 布拉德
Of course I trust you,Brad.

18:27.580 --> 18:31.100
不过要是被人知道的话 我...
It's just that if anybody finds out about this,I...

18:31.110 --> 18:31.900
没人会知道的
They won't.

18:37.080 --> 18:37.920
交给我了
Let me handle this.

18:44.030 --> 18:46.470
大胖子 死胖子 爬上一堵墙
Humpty Dumpty climbed up a wall.

18:47.100 --> 18:49.660
大胖子 死胖子 重重摔下来
Humpty Dumpty had a great fall.

18:51.780 --> 18:52.410
听着
Look...

18:52.770 --> 18:55.190
我已经告诉过联邦探员 我什么都不知道了
I already told the feds I don't know anything,okay?

18:55.200 --> 18:57.050
他们衣冠楚楚 文质彬彬
Those suits with pedicures and penny loafers.

18:57.060 --> 18:58.350
你当然不会说
Why would you?

18:58.820 --> 19:00.920
他们循规蹈矩
They have rules to follow,codes of conduct.

19:00.930 --> 19:02.480
他们要保住饭碗
They got jobs to protect.

19:03.520 --> 19:04.760
而我不一样
Now me,on the other hand.

19:04.770 --> 19:05.650
拜托老大
Come on,Boss.

19:06.180 --> 19:06.780
我发誓
I swear.

19:07.380 --> 19:09.240
这群家伙没让我参与计划
Those guys didn't let me in on any plans.

19:09.620 --> 19:13.590
那你是说 你们每次开会
Then you're telling me in all your little powwows in the yard

19:14.270 --> 19:16.490
他们都没说过
they never once mentioned what they were going to do

19:16.500 --> 19:17.960
逃出去以后有什么打算吗?
once they went over that wall?

19:17.970 --> 19:18.950
没错
That's right.

19:25.000 --> 19:25.740
现在...
Now...

19:26.670 --> 19:29.160
我已经不在这里上班了 大胖子
I may not work here anymore,Big-uns,

19:29.840 --> 19:32.010
但我在这里还是有些影响力的
but I still got influence with people who do,

19:32.020 --> 19:34.270
我说什么他们就会照做
people who will do whatever I ask them to

19:35.090 --> 19:37.310
要他们整谁他们就去整谁
to whoever I ask them to.

19:41.170 --> 19:42.150
还有...
And a...

19:42.950 --> 19:49.360
像你这样凹凸有致的身材
well,let's just say there's some filthy individuals

19:49.370 --> 19:51.100
这么说吧  牢里有些变态
who might enjoy a cellie

19:51.100 --> 19:53.240
最喜欢你这种有女人味的了
with womanly attributes.

19:57.290 --> 19:59.900
把你知道的都说出来
Now,you're going to tell me everything you know

20:01.310 --> 20:03.300
告诉我 他们要去哪
about where those convicts are headed,

20:04.960 --> 20:08.420
否则我就把你扔去喂色狼
or I'm going to throw your fat ass to the wolves.

20:13.930 --> 20:14.920
好 谢谢
Okay,thanks.

20:15.790 --> 20:18.220
第3个错误  有人报告说看到一个
Mistake number three: someone reported seeing

20:18.220 --> 20:21.710
貌似费尔南多 苏克雷的人偷了辆车
a man matching Fernando Sucre's description stealing a car.

20:21.710 --> 20:22.500
在哪儿?
Where?

20:22.510 --> 20:25.250
俄亥俄州的迪非恩斯
Defiance,Ohio.

20:27.490 --> 20:28.630
今天有人要落网了
Someone's going down today.

20:37.000 --> 20:38.800
我知道  圣母  我知道
I know,<i>mami, I know.

20:50.320 --> 20:53.730
莎拉... 我替你付了保释金了
Sara... I paid your bail.

20:53.730 --> 20:55.010
你可以再晚一点来
You took your time.

20:56.030 --> 20:56.840
我是州长
I'm the governor.

20:56.850 --> 20:58.620
-我有很多事情要处理...  -省省吧
I do have things that... Go to hell,Dad.

20:59.830 --> 21:00.680
你要是再这样
You keep this up,

21:00.690 --> 21:03.080
就别想出去了
this may be the only place I'll be able to see you.

21:03.730 --> 21:05.840
你不想知道我的解释吗?
Do you even want to hear my side of things?

21:05.850 --> 21:07.260
不想知道  莎拉
Not particularly,Sara,no.

21:08.440 --> 21:11.930
特别是现在我都不知道你算哪一边的
Especially when I have no idea whose "side" you're on.

21:12.710 --> 21:13.740
但是我知道一件事
But I do know this.

21:14.720 --> 21:17.820
总要有人要为福克斯河的事承担责任
Somebody is going to go down because of what happened at Fox River.

21:18.400 --> 21:20.520
如果不是你的话
And it would be in both of our best interests

21:20.530 --> 21:22.220
对我们两个人都好
if that someone was not you.

21:22.830 --> 21:25.090
为了确保这个  我们必须采取些措施
And to ensure this,certain steps need to be taken.

21:25.100 --> 21:25.850
首先
One:

21:26.590 --> 21:28.470
你要去参加座谈会
you should go to a daily recovery meeting.

21:28.480 --> 21:29.080
其次
Two:

21:29.080 --> 21:30.800
你需要在审理前就去参加
you need to go before a judge

21:30.810 --> 21:32.430
并且宣称无罪  还有...
and plead not guilty,and three,

21:32.430 --> 21:33.190
爸爸  我不...

21:33.190 --> 21:34.560
你必须告诉惩戒署
you need to tell the D.O.C.

21:35.130 --> 21:37.810
你对他们越狱知之甚少
everything you know about how that prison was being run.

21:38.370 --> 21:39.580
还有 珀尔狱长的事
And that Warden Pope,

21:39.590 --> 21:41.270
因为斯科菲尔德帮他作私事
how he was granting favors to Scofield

21:41.280 --> 21:43.720
他就给与斯科菲尔德特权
because Scofield helped him with his personal projects,

21:43.730 --> 21:46.470
让他方便到达管制区域
thereby exposing him to certain restricted areas

21:46.470 --> 21:47.750
从而使他有机会
where he may have been able

21:47.760 --> 21:49.730
拿到医务室的钥匙
to obtain a key to the infirmary.

21:51.930 --> 21:53.020
我不能那么做
I can't do that.

21:53.710 --> 21:54.850
可以 你可以的  莎拉.
Oh,yes you can,Sara.

21:54.860 --> 21:56.320
你可以  你必须这么做
You can do that and you will.

21:57.500 --> 21:58.610
是我干的  爸爸
I did it,Dad.

22:02.010 --> 22:04.630
我没有关门  不是别人
I left the door open,me and no one else.

22:05.670 --> 22:06.600
那不是真的
That's not true.

22:07.520 --> 22:08.370
是真的
Yes,it is.

22:08.380 --> 22:09.700
那不是真的
That's not true.

22:12.420 --> 22:13.200
莎拉...
Sara...

22:15.320 --> 22:16.840
就照我说的去做
just do what you're told,

22:18.270 --> 22:21.230
否则后果会很严重...
otherwise there will be consequences...

22:22.520 --> 22:23.790
我们都会被影响到的
that will affect us all.

22:24.950 --> 22:26.710
你知道我的意思吗?
Do you understand what I'm telling you?

22:28.210 --> 22:28.920
明白
Yes,sir.

22:30.140 --> 22:30.870
很好
Good.

22:34.800 --> 22:36.740
再过一星期... 我会被任命为

22:36.740 --> 22:39.430
新一任的美国副总统
the new Vice President of the United States.

22:39.430 --> 22:41.330
他们会举办一个庆典  会邀请你
There will be a ceremony,you will be invited,

22:42.720 --> 22:43.910
但是你却不能出席
but you will not attend.

22:47.460 --> 22:48.300
再见  莎拉

23:04.840 --> 23:07.250
-我们听点音乐吧  -不行
Let's put some music on. Don't.

23:07.260 --> 23:08.010
我忘了
I forgot.

23:08.390 --> 23:09.090
不能听电台
No radio.

23:11.320 --> 23:12.420
这里太静了
Man,it's quiet out here.

23:12.430 --> 23:15.300
里面一直都很吵
Inside,there was always noise,you know?

23:15.680 --> 23:17.520
总有人喊叫  守卫们四处巡逻
Someone yelling,guards making rounds.

23:17.520 --> 23:18.440
我都已经习惯了
I got used to it.

23:19.650 --> 23:20.310
没错
You're right.

