They're saying you're on TV because you're a bad man.

28:21.100 --> 28:22.050
那你怎么想呢
And what do you think?

28:23.700 --> 28:27.410
我想 如果我在一个不能看到你的地方
I think if I were someplace and they wouldn't let me

28:27.410 --> 28:30.520
