Well,you know what?

28:36.850 --> 28:38.610
我们很快就能在一起了
We are gonna be together real soon.

28:39.200 --> 28:40.290
我向你保证
I promise you.

28:40.930 --> 28:42.640
但是你要帮爸爸个忙
But Daddy needs you to do him a favor.

28:42.650 --> 28:44.460
我要你给妈妈带个口信  好吗
I need you to get a message to Mommy,okay?

28:45.210 --> 28:45.830
好的
Okay.

28:47.330 --> 28:48.490
我需要你去告诉她
Now I need you to tell her

28:48.500 --> 28:51.070
如果她明白我告诉她的事
if she understood what <i>I told her

28:52.020 --> 28:53.920
而且愿意相信爸爸的话
and if she is willing to trust Daddy...

28:57.260 --> 28:58.920
那么就在7点
that she needs to turn on the porch light

28:59.820 --> 29:02.070
打开门廊的灯
at 7:00,okay?

29:03.070 --> 29:04.090
你能记住吗
Can you remember that?

29:04.800 --> 29:05.700
好样的
That's a good girl.

29:06.400 --> 29:07.150
蒂蒂
Dede,

29:07.160 --> 29:08.540
离围栏远一点  宝贝
stay away from the gate,honey.

29:11.870 --> 29:13.640
爸爸要走了  好吗  小宝贝
Daddy gotta get going,okay sweet pea?

29:17.250 --> 29:18.380
我爱你  爸爸
I love you,Daddy.

29:19.380 --> 29:20.650
我也爱你  宝贝
I love you,too,baby.

29:30.400 --> 29:31.000
那边
There.

29:39.510 --> 29:40.710
不远了
It's not much further now.

29:51.470 --> 29:52.410
好的  他们转出州际公路 目前向北开
Okay,they moved off

29:52.420 --> 29:55.620
- 在38号公路上  - 请说
the Interstate,heading North on Route 38. Talk to me.

29:58.080 --> 29:58.620
在哪儿
Where?

30:00.040 --> 30:01.320
有一个巡警报告说
There's a patrolman who thinks he's has

30:01.330 --> 30:03.900
他在宾州的拉特罗布截停了 苏克雷·费尔南多的车了
Fernando Sucre pulled over outside of Latrobe,Pennsylvania.

30:03.900 --> 30:05.620
联系当地警局
Get in touch with the local dispatch.

30:05.630 --> 30:07.730
告诉他们  我们要活捉这个人
Make it clear that we want this man in custody,

30:07.730 --> 30:09.060
不是死尸
not in a body bag.

30:09.760 --> 30:11.550
死人告诉不了我们他的朋友在哪
Dead men can't tell us where their friends are.

30:11.930 --> 30:12.680
是的 明白了
Yeah,you got it.

30:55.910 --> 30:57.330
应该是的 长得一样
It's gotta be,it looks just like him.

30:57.330 --> 30:59.150
好的 我来处理
Yeah,I'll take care of it.

30:59.160 --> 31:00.710
我会的
I will.

