米勒先生...
Mr. Miller...

31:14.070 --> 31:17.760
请你将手伸出车外
I'm gonna have to ask you to place your arms outside the vehicle please.

31:20.210 --> 31:22.100
米勒先生 把手伸出来
Mr. Miller,I need to see some hands.

31:57.810 --> 31:58.450
准备好了吗?
You ready?

31:59.130 --> 31:59.800
好了
Yeah.

32:02.260 --> 32:02.830
现在
Now.

32:17.810 --> 32:18.650
就是这儿了
This is the one.

32:26.970 --> 32:28.300
- 看到他了么?   - 没
Do you see him? Nope.

32:28.820 --> 32:29.780
也许他没收到你的消息
Maybe he didn't get your message.

32:40.450 --> 32:41.430
他们停下来了
They've stopped.

32:42.500 --> 32:43.970
前面几英里处 那儿...
Couple miles up ahead. There's...

32:44.970 --> 32:46.080
那儿没什么特别的啊 他们...
There's nothing up there. What...?

32:47.160 --> 32:47.980
他们在等什么?
What are they waiting on?

32:49.240 --> 32:49.980
或是等什么人?
Or who?

32:56.530 --> 32:58.480
好的 很好 很好
All right,that's good,that's good,

33:20.510 --> 33:21.780
哦 快点
Oh,come on.

33:22.390 --> 33:23.220
快点!
Come on!

33:26.270 --> 33:27.070
亮警灯
Go red.

33:27.770 --> 33:28.960
快 警灯!
Now,go red!

33:56.240 --> 33:57.060
还有一件事
Just one more thing.

33:59.590 --> 34:00.320
你相信我么
Do you trust me?

34:03.490 --> 34:04.310
当然
Of course.

34:05.490 --> 34:07.490
有什么办法可以让猎人放弃追踪？
