34:08.480 --> 34:09.380
毁掉猎物
Get rid of the prey.

34:10.880 --> 34:13.240
记住 按下电台扫描后
Remember,once I hit scan,

34:13.240 --> 34:15.640
在搜到103.7之前我们约有30秒的时间
we'll have about 30 seconds before it reaches 103.7.

34:15.640 --> 34:16.510
然后就爆炸了？
And then she blows?

34:17.410 --> 34:19.170
是的 准备好了没？
That's right. Ready?

34:19.170 --> 34:19.940
是的
Yeah.

34:39.580 --> 34:40.260
好了 我们闪
All right,let's go.

