出问题了
Something's wrong.

34:54.070 --> 34:54.770
怎么了
What happened?

34:55.870 --> 34:56.640
我也不知道
I don't know.

34:57.290 --> 34:58.440
一定要让它爆炸
But we're going to need the explosion.

