35:16.460 --> 35:17.900
我们必须手动调
We're going to have to set it off manually.

35:18.520 --> 35:19.810
车随时会爆炸
The car could blow any second,Michael.

35:20.280 --> 35:22.120
探员两分钟内就到了
Well,the feds are going to be here in about two minutes.

35:23.170 --> 35:24.820
如果不能伪装成事故  我们就死定了
If it doesn't look like we're dead,we will be.

35:25.850 --> 35:26.810
剪刀 石头 布
Rock,paper,scissors?

35:27.890 --> 35:28.570
林肯?
Linc?

