该我上了
It's my turn.

35:46.390 --> 35:47.470
但愿能收到信号
Better pray for reception.

35:56.960 --> 36:00.520
102.1和103.7之间有几个台？
How many stations between 102.1 and 103.7?

36:01.120 --> 36:01.870
在这收台？
Way out here?

36:03.100 --> 36:04.660
可能只有一个
Just one,probably.

36:46.200 --> 36:47.170
玛丽克鲁兹在哪?
Where's Maricruz?

36:47.860 --> 36:48.580
嘿 老兄听着
Hey. Hey,look,man...

36:48.590 --> 36:50.070
不 不不 佩特你听着
No,no,no,Petey. <i>You look.

36:50.080 --> 36:52.300
我已经72个小时没睡了
I haven't slept in 72 hours,

36:52.300 --> 36:54.250
我亲眼看着一个人的手被剁掉
I've seen a man's hand get chopped off,

36:54.260 --> 36:57.010
我被人用枪指着 挖过坟墓
I've been... I've been shot at,dug up a grave,

36:57.010 --> 36:58.950
偷了辆车 还扒了趟火车
stolen a car,jumped on a fricking a train,

36:59.930 --> 37:01.740
求你告诉我 她在哪里
so please,just tell me where she is.

37:01.740 --> 37:03.960
费尔南多 冷静下来
Hey,Fernando,slow down,man.

37:03.960 --> 37:06.460
我正要告诉你 可你没听我说完就挂电话了
I was trying to tell you,but you hung up the phone,man.

37:06.470 --> 37:08.160
婚礼在维加斯举行
The wedding-- it's in Vegas.

37:10.590 --> 37:11.370
拉斯维加斯？
The city?

37:11.370 --> 37:14.280
是的 几小时前 他们刚刚离开
Yeah,and they left a few hours ago.

37:24.360 --> 37:25.850
等等 别 别冲动
Wait,no,no,no.

37:25.850 --> 37:28.030
别这样 嘿 费尔南多
Come on,hey,come on. Fernando!

37:28.420 --> 37:29.790
这可是经典老款...
It's pristine,man. It's just...

37:29.790 --> 37:32.150
我保证会完好无损的还给你
Gonna be back to you in one piece,I promise.

37:32.150 --> 37:35.590
- 我还没说要借给你呢 - 我也是别无选择
Can we go back to the partwhere I said no? I wish I had another choice.

37:35.610 --> 37:36.940
你当然有路可选
You do have a choice.

37:36.940 --> 37:41.500
这是1952年乌拉尔牌摩托车
Come on,man. It's a 1952 Ural motorbike,bro

37:41.510 --> 37:42.800
如果你敢刮伤它
If you so much as scratch it...

37:42.810 --> 37:44.660
我保证不会刮伤的
No scratches... I promise.

37:47.780 --> 37:50.250
她是我生命中的最爱
She's the love of my life,bro.

37:51.000 --> 37:51.960
我必须采取行动
I got to do something.

37:52.790 --> 37:53.780
你是鬼上身了
You look like hell.

37:54.190 --> 37:55.580
我刚从地狱回来
I've been through hell,

37:56.180 --> 37:59.000
现在我要去拉斯维加斯
Now I just got to get to Vegas.

38:07.190 --> 38:09.420
嗨 我是莎拉
Um,hi,I'm Sara,

38:09.430 --> 38:10.620
我 嗯...
and I,uh...

38:14.270 --> 38:15.090
嗯...
Um...

38:18.920 --> 38:24.090
