over the years,I've worked with...more than a few people who had a history of addiction,

38:24.610 --> 38:27.260
嗯...
and,uh...

38:27.270 --> 38:28.740
我会告诉他们我可以理解
I would tell them that I could understand

38:28.750 --> 38:30.480
他们的感受 因为我...
what they were going through,because I...

38:32.040 --> 38:33.440
过去曾和他们一样
used to be just like them.

38:33.440 --> 38:35.640
我也曾是个瘾君子
I used to be an addict,too.

38:36.870 --> 38:38.590
我想...
And I think,uh...

38:41.040 --> 38:43.250
我心里很清楚
I think that what's becoming clear to me

38:43.260 --> 38:44.430
就是...
is that...

38:45.520 --> 38:46.700
