39:25.700 --> 39:26.730
真可悲
Kind of sad really.

39:27.870 --> 39:29.050
出事的是谁?
So,which one of them was it?

39:33.300 --> 39:34.050
希尔斯
Shales.

39:35.150 --> 39:35.960
希尔斯?
Shales?

39:36.660 --> 39:37.660
斯科菲尔德
S-Scofield.

39:37.660 --> 39:38.600
也许是斯科菲尔德
Might be Scofield.

39:39.370 --> 39:41.120
或许还可以从残骸里找到他的哥哥
You're probably going to find his brother in there,too.

39:43.530 --> 39:45.940
奥斯卡 希尔斯 是不是那个马宏追了很久的家伙
Oscar Shales is this guy Mahone tracked for a while.

39:46.310 --> 39:47.580
